    so a gqlgen resolver is a one-liner.

The matching `.graphql` schema fragment (`union X = A | B`) is
written to the file configured via entpoly.WithGQLSchemaFile(...).
Without that extension option the user must declare the union in
their .graphql by hand. See docs/laravel-parity.md and the FAQ. */ -}}
